Package: cindexdecomp
Title: C-Index Decomposition for Survival Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Malik J.", "Lainsbury", , "mjl221@cam.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Decomposes Harrell's Concordance Index into Event-Event 
    and Event-Censored components to expose performance masking in 
    highly censored survival data.
